hopobject.body: About a year virility reviews Currently, the e-cigarette industry is not allowed to make medical claims for their products, for example retailers can’t refer to them as a way to quit smoking. It has been suggested that if they were to be regulated as a medical product, they could be offered on the NHS. Attempts to classify e-ciggies as medical products have been made across the channel in Holland and Germany but the industry shot them down in court.
